<p><b>What is the key concept of housekeeping?</b> Housekeeping refers to the management and organization of domestic or commercial spaces to maintain cleanliness, order, and a pleasant environment. It involves a range of activities and tasks that are performed to keep living spaces, offices, hotels, or other establishments clean, tidy, and well-maintained.</p>
